# Hospital Management System

A web-based Hospital Management System developed using ASP.NET (C#), HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  
The application manages patients, doctors, staff, and appointments with secure authentication and SQL Server database integration to streamline hospital operations and reduce manual work.

## Technologies Used
- ASP.NET (C#)
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- SQL Server
- Entity Framework

## Features
- User authentication
- Patient, doctor, and staff management
- Appointment scheduling
- Admin dashboard
- CRUD operations

